---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="CONTACT">

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium text-center text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Contact Us</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-center mb-4">お問い合わせ</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mb-12">採用以外のご質問・ご相談もお気軽にどうぞ。</p>

      <form class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-8 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">お名前 <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <input type="text" required placeholder="橋本 章平"
            class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">メールアドレス <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" required placeholder="example@email.com"
            class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">お問い合わせ種別</label>
          <select class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition bg-white">
            <option>採用について</option>
            <option>事業・サービスについて</option>
            <option>取材・メディア</option>
            <option>その他</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">メッセージ <span class="text-red-500">*</span></label>
          <textarea required rows="5" placeholder="お問い合わせ内容をご記入ください"
            class="w-full border border-gray-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition resize-none"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit"
          class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors text-sm">
          送信する →
        </button>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center">
          いただいた内容は2営業日以内にご返信いたします。
        </p>
      </form>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
        <p>採用エントリーはこちら →</p>
        <a href="/recruit" class="inline-block mt-2 text-blue-600 font-bold hover:underline">採用情報ページへ</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
